						<h2 class="pagetitle">Function Reference/load child theme textdomain</h2>
									<!-- start content -->
				<div style="clear:both; background-color:#FCECAD; border:1px solid #CCCCCC; color:#000000; padding:7px; margin:0.5em auto 0.5em auto; vertical-align:middle;">This article is a <a href="/Category:Drafts" title="Category:Drafts">ROUGH DRAFT</a>.  The author is still working on this document, so <b>please do not edit this without the author's permission</b>. The content within this article may not yet be verified or valid.  This information is subject to change.</div>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents"><tr><td><div id="toctitle"><h2>Contents</h2></div>
<ul>
